Package: backports
Type: Package
Title: Some backports of functions introduced since R-3.0.0
Version: 1.0
Author: Michel Lang <michellang@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Michel Lang <michellang@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides functions which have been introduced in one
    of the base packages in R version 3.0.1 or later.
    The functions are conditionally exported in order to let R resolve the
    function name to the implemented backport only if the respective base
    version is not available.
License: GPL-2
NeedsCompilation: no
ByteCompile: yes
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
